In order to run the code on Linux machine, the only requirement is that the JVM should be installed on the machine.

Input:
The file to be passed as input should be placed in Resource folder and name of the file should be passes as a Command line Argument to main() method.
Example : "Test.txt" as an argument to the program

Test Cases:
A doc as well as pdf file is present in the src folder mentioning different scenarios that have been tested.